snippet.title: Personal Branding within a Company | Ashley amber Hughes
snippet.description:
Join us this week as Ashley Amber Hughes goes into how shes was able to create her own personal brand working for a company. Ashley talks about joining the marketing world and how she got started. She also talk her push notification business, Pushnami, and how it works. You are not going to want to miss out on this weeks episode!


Reach out to her on: LinkedIn// Ashley Amber Hughes


If you haven't gotten a chance please give us a rating on itunes...it  would be greatly appreciate to help us stand out! 


Find more on Burkhart  Creative Agency: Instagram//@burkhartcreativeagency LinkedIn//@Steven   Burkhart Website// http://www.burkhartcreativeagency.com. 



I will personally get back to you!
